<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Your Testimonial - React Fast Training</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0ea5e9 0%, #10b981 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 32px 24px;
        }
        .thank-you-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff 0%, #ecfdf5 100%);
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }
        .thank-you-box h2 {
            color: #0ea5e9;
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .thank-you-box p {
            color: #374151;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .testimonial-preview {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
        }
        .testimonial-content {
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .rating {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .star {
            color: #fbbf24;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .star.empty {
            color: #d1d5db;
        }
        .submission-details {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .submission-details h3 {
            margin: 0 0 16px 0;
            color: #1f2937;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .detail-value {
            color: #1f2937;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .photo-status {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border: 1px solid #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #92400e;
        }
        .photo-status.included {
            background-color: #d1fae5;
            border-color: #10b981;
            color: #065f46;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .next-steps h3 {
            color: #1e40af;
            margin: 0 0 12px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .next-steps ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .next-steps li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 0;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .company-info {
            margin-top: 16px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        .social-links a {
            color: #0ea5e9;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 8px;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 4px;
            }
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üåü Thank You!</h1>
            <p>Your testimonial has been received</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="thank-you-box">
                <h2>We Appreciate Your Feedback</h2>
                <p>
                    Thank you {{authorName}} for taking the time to share your experience with React Fast Training. 
                    Your feedback helps us improve our services and helps others make informed decisions about their first aid training.
                </p>
            </div>

            <h3 style="color: #1f2937; margin-bottom: 16px;">üìã Your Testimonial Submission</h3>
            
            <div class="testimonial-preview">
                <div class="rating">
                    {{#each stars}}
                        <span class="star{{#unless this}} empty{{/unless}}">‚òÖ</span>
                    {{/each}}
                    <span style="margin-left: 8px; font-weight: 600;">{{rating}}/5 Stars</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="testimonial-content">
                    "{{content}}"
                </div>
                
                <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; color: #374151;">
                    ‚Äî {{authorName}}{{#if authorLocation}}, {{authorLocation}}{{/if}}
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="submission-details">
                <h3>Submission Details</h3>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Course Taken:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{courseTaken}}</span>
                </div>
                
                {{#if courseDate}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Course Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{courseDate}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                {{#if bookingReference}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Booking Reference:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{bookingReference}}</span>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Full Name Display:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{#if showFullName}}Yes{{else}}First name + initial only{{/if}}</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Submitted:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{submittedAt}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            {{#if hasPhoto}}
                <div class="photo-status included">
                    üì∏ <strong>Photo Included:</strong> Your photo has been attached to this email.
                    {{#if photoConsent}}
                        You have given consent for us to use this photo on our website and marketing materials.
                    {{else}}
                        You have chosen not to give consent for public use of this photo.
                    {{/if}}
                </div>
            {{else}}
                <div class="photo-status">
                    üì∑ <strong>No Photo:</strong> You did not include a photo with this testimonial.
                </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What Happens Next?</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Our team will review your testimonial within 1-2 business days</li>
                    <li>If approved, your testimonial may be featured on our website</li>
                    <li>We respect your display preferences and photo consent choices</li>
                    <li>You may be contacted if we need any clarification</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 32px; padding: 16px; background-color: #f0f9ff; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; text-align: center;">
                <strong>Questions?</strong> If you have any questions about your submission, please contact us at 
                <a href="mailto:info@reactfasttraining.co.uk" style="color: #0ea5e9;">info@reactfasttraining.co.uk</a> 
                or call <strong>07447 485644</strong>.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>React Fast Training</strong> - Yorkshire's Premier First Aid Training Provider</p>
            <div class="company-info">
                üìß info@reactfasttraining.co.uk | üìû 07447 485644<br>
                üåê reactfasttraining.co.uk<br>
                Serving Leeds, Sheffield, Bradford, York, Huddersfield, Wakefield, Halifax, Harrogate
            </div>
            <div class="social-links">
                <p style="margin: 16px 0 8px 0; color: #6b7280;">Stay Connected:</p>
                <a href="https://reactfasttraining.co.uk">Visit Our Website</a>
            </div>
            <p style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af;">
                This email was sent to {{authorEmail}} as confirmation of your testimonial submission.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>